All Implemented Interfaces:
Shape, Serializable, Cloneable
public class EPGYRectangle
extends Rectangle2D.Double

This class is a data structure for storing rectangles. There are a number of useful operations like finding intersections and checking for the inclusion of points.

Author:
Matthew Chun-Lum
